Package: MetaboMate
Type: Package
Title: The R toolbox for NMR-based metabolic profiling.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Kimhofer", "Torben", email = "tkimhofer@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Holmes", "Elaine", role = c("exp", "rth")),
  person("Nicholson", "Jeremy K.", role = c("exp", "rth")),
  person("Li", "Jia V.", role = c("exp", "rth")),
  person("Wist", "Julian", role = c("exp", "rtm", "ctb")))
Maintainer: Torben Kimhofer <tkimhofer@gmail.com>
Description: R toolbox for NMR-based metabolic profiling. Comprehensive library that covers all basic steps of the metabolic profiling analysis pipeline. This includes reading-in 1D spectra from Bruker file format, data pre-processing, various normalisation methods, unsupervised and supervised multivariate analysis techniques and feature extraction. Most of the provided functions can also be used for MS data analysis (such as PQN normalisation or O-PLS). All combined with aestethically pleasing visualisations using ggplot2.
